  roomName: dragon
  description: The smog grows dense. It's hard to breath as you step into the room
    and watch the skulls dangling on the long string over the pit of fire rattle.
    The dragon raises its head with a laugh before lowering it to face you, flames
    tickling its mouth
  altDescription: The smog has fallen to a rest. The corpse of the dragon lays as
    if a fallen puppet. They are of no threat to you. It seems their corpse has crushed
    the way back though, you may need to go another route
